  "keyFeatures": [
    "Single Rust binary with <5MB RAM footprint and <10ms cold start",
    "Trait-driven architecture: swap providers, channels, tools, and memory with config changes",
    "Secure-by-default: gateway pairing, sandbox, filesystem scoping, encrypted secrets",
    "70+ channel integrations (Telegram, Discord, Slack, WhatsApp, Matrix, Signal, and more)",
    "Built-in hybrid memory search engine (SQLite FTS5 + vector embeddings)",
    "Fully autonomous daemon mode with scheduled tasks (heartbeat, cron)",
    "OpenAI-compatible and Anthropic-compatible custom provider endpoints",
    "Hardware peripheral support (STM32, Raspberry Pi GPIO, USB discovery)",
    "Python companion package (zeroclaw-tools) with LangGraph-based tool calling",
    "AIEOS identity system support for portable AI personas"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
